---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const badgeItems = [
	{
		label: 'React',
		iconUrl: '/react_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Vue',
		iconUrl: '/vue_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Inertiajs',
		iconUrl: '/react_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Laravel',
		iconUrl: '/react_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Svelte',
		iconUrl: '/svelte_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Astro',
		iconUrl: '/astro_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Symfony',
		iconUrl: '/react_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Supabase',
		iconUrl: '/react_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Nextjs',
		iconUrl: '/nextjs_icon.png',
	},
	{
		label: 'Nuxtjs',
		iconUrl: '/nuxtjs_icon.webp',
	}
]
---
<Layout>
	<div class="pt-10">
		<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Hi there ðŸ‘‹ </h1>

		<p class="pt-5 leading-8 text-gray-700 text-lg max-w-2xl">
			My name is Vincent Dorian. I am a <strong>Full-stack developer</strong> building stuff that I like.
			When I got my first job after graduating in 2021, I started working in web development. Since then my work has become my hobby and passion.
		</p>

		<p class="pt-5 leading-8 text-gray-700 text-lg max-w-2xl">
			I have full time working experience in the languages PHP and Javascript, working with different frameworks like React, Vue, Svelte and more.
			<strong>Inertiajs</strong> and <strong>Laravel</strong> are my tools of choice to build my backends and I love working with <strong>Tailwindcss.</strong>
		</p>

		<p class="pt-5 leading-8 text-gray-700 text-lg max-w-2xl">
			Feel free to stay a little while, if you want to find out more <a href="/about-me"><strong class="underline">about me</strong></a>. In my <a href="/blog"><strong class="underline">my blog</strong></a> I am reflecting on some of the things, I encounter in my free time. 
			The processes of my projects are documented in my <a href="/journal"><strong class="underline">journal.</strong></a>
		</p>

		<p class="pt-5 leading-8 text-gray-700 text-lg max-w-2xl">
			If you would like to get in touch, you can contact me on <strong class="underline"><a href="mailto:hi@vincentdorian.me">hi@vincentdorian.me</a></strong> or connect with me on social media.
						</p>

	</div>

	<div class="mt-3">
		<span class="block font-medium text-lg">
			Here is a list of the technologies I am familiar with:
		</span>
		<div class="flex flex-row gap-2 flex-wrap">
			{
				badgeItems.map((item) => (
					<span class="inline-flex pl-2 pr-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-gray-50 border-gray-200 gap-x-2 border font-medium items-center">
						<img src={item.iconUrl} class="h-5 flex-shrink-0">
						{item.label}
						</span>
				))
			}
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>